race.name: STP 500
race.comments: Brad Keselowski won the 70th Annual STP 500 at Martinsville Speedway, his 29th victory in the Monster Energy NASCAR Cup Series. Prior to the start of the race, the following cars dropped to the rear of the field under penalty for the reasons indicated: Nos. 32, 51 (backup car); Nos. 24, 77, 52 (inspection failure).
